name: Pondok Salam PSJ Jerman
address: HJ74+3MH, Jln. Serial Natih, Karangasem, Kec. Karangasem, Kabupaten Karangasem, Bali, Indonesia
review 1:
Came here after a long drive and was very heartened to see an opened eatery in the middle of the day.

Location is a 10/10 because the ventilation is so breezy, and the view is simply amazing. Oversees a beautiful paddy & vegatable field and Mount Agung.

Food wise is very mediocre. Small meat and large carb portions. Fried chicken was pretty ok! Iced tea was refreshing.
review 2: Great view and great price, food was tastier than in other places around the area. Really recommend!
